{"tid":2261663,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"求旅遊節目推薦 #adore","createTime":"2020-10-28T13:22:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T14:26:21.000Z","uid":89595,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"50a399bb88ed509fce07721b103ec3aeaca9713c","tid":2261663,"uid":89595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:22:02.000Z","msg":"喺屋企坐到悶想睇下啲旅行show解下癮<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/stretching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幾個要求 要英文／有英文字幕嘅 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最好長少少，起碼廿分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔prefer淨係得一個theme (飲食／購物/火車 etc..) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網可以搵到 Netflix Amazon Prime Youtube 呢啲平台就最好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋唔想要啲好老餅嘅，好似 Rick Steves' Europe 嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n細個喺明珠台睇講意大利嗰啲幾好但搵唔返了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n即使係YouTuber嗰啲都冇咩所謂，好似ming仔嗰類其實唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係唔想要太vlog類，即係Sam Kolder, Yes theory嗰啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Bob叔郵輪片 酒店片都ok 其他旅行片真係唔掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開過喺旅遊台不過冇乜反應 希望呢邊全能嘅巴絲可以幫到我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a4b9fe01627f0f65fbd6dbf41267c5f55dcee64","tid":2261663,"uid":246262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T13:49:57.000Z","msg":"Netflix most dangerous jail in the world 乜乜乜"},{"pid":"8a05ed4638b73164e85169504ca9862331fb72a4","tid":2261663,"uid":299187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-28T14:06:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3tPJGDv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3tPJGDv.jpg&h=65ff0e07&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"39e802d4858a